results.name: Steps until an EKG sequence starting 1,2,3,...,n merges with the standard EKG sequence A064413, or 0 if the sequences never merge.
example: a(5)=11 because that EKG sequence starts 1,2,3,4,5,10,6,8,12,9,15 and from the 11th term onwards it is the same as A064413.
results.author: _Martin Fuller_, Jul 26 2006
